  "name": "Avani Ibn Battuta Dubai Hotel",
  "description": "Right beside Dubai Metro, superb shopping right on your doorstep and a dizzying array of exciting activities. Only 30 minutes drive from both Dubai International Airport and Dubai World Central airport, Avani Ibn Battuta Dubai Hotel is situated in a well-developed part of the city. The Dubai Metro is accessible via the Ibn Battuta Metro Link, just next door, connecting visitors to the financial district, cultural hotspots and the tallest building in the world, Burj Khalifa. For relaxation, guests can take a short taxi to the golden sands of the Arabian Gulf or explore entertainment options such as a state-of-the-art cinema and bowling alley just a few minutes away on foot. Avani Ibn Battuta Dubai Hotel is an ideal base for Expo 2020. Whether business or pleasure, guests will find a convenient city escape under our roof. When you want to work, play and sleep your way, we take care of the details that matter.",
